                                    <p>FedEx ships more than <a href="https://about.van.fedex.com/our-story/company-structure/corporate-fact-sheet/" target="_blank">14 million packages</a> each business day, and rival carrier UPS ships <a href="https://pressroom.ups.com/pressroom/ContentDetailsViewer.page?ConceptType=FactSheets&id=1426321563187-193" target="_blank">20 million packages and documents</a> daily. </p>
                                    <p>
