                                    </p>
                                    <p>
                                        But as a business owner, <b>how can you rest assured that you’re getting the best shipping rates? </b> </p>
                                        <p>
                                            You may be enticed by introductory discounts which only last for a limited time (i.e. FedEx’s Advantage Program discounts on select Ground, Office, and Express services), or you might simply accept the rates you’re given without protest.  </P>
                                    <p>
                                    However, for a business that ships constantly and whose needs are ever-evolving, <b>you don’t have to settle for the first offer.  You can negotiate.</b>
                                     </p>
                                   
